  <summary date="2018-07-26T04:00:00Z" status="Introduced in House">Sex Offender Registration and Victim Protection Act of 2018

This bill requires aliens who are registered sex offenders and are subject to removal to provide additional information for inclusion in the sex offender registry, including the alien's registration number, country of nationality, immigration status, and biometric information.</summary>
